    {
      "Text": "Security update for agama",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for agama fixes the following issue\n\n- CVE-2026-25727: time: parsing of user-provided input by the RFC 2822 date parser can lead to stack exhaustion\n  (bsc#1257930).\n\nChanges for agama:\n\n- Update \"time\" crate to version 0.3.47.\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
